title: AP Computer Science Project - Maikel Abadir

json.text: Hello This is Maikel Abadir and my program is a remake of the popular game, "Hangman"
My program is written in Java Script using the App Lab in "code.org"
The purpose of my program is just a fun game anyone can play
In this video, you will see what happens when I lose the game, and what happens when I win the game
In this first example, I lose the game because all the hangman body parts were drawn before I was able to click the correct letters
In this second example, I was able to click on all the correct letters before the hangman was drawn
